1 - ENTANGLE (A, 1m, c): Difficult terrain in 20' sq w/i 90'. STR save or Restrained
1 - ABSORB ELEMENT (R): Resist acid/cold/fire/lightning/thunder & +1d6 next melee
2 - MOONBEAM (A, 1m, c): 5'r 40'H fills w/dim light. 2d10 radiant or CON save for 1/2
1 - FAERIE FIRE (A, 1m, c): 20' cube w/i 60', DEX or outlined & face Adv on attacks
2 - HEAT METAL (A, 1m, c): A metal obj w/i 60' - 2d8 fire + (CON & drops) or DisAdv
1 - HEALING WORD (BA): Regain 1d4 + Mod to creature w/i 60'
3 - SPEAK W/PLANTS (A, 10m): plants w/i 30' talk & follow commands. Switch terrain
2 - PASS W/O TRACE (A, 1hr, c): all allies w/i 30' get +10 to Stealth checks
3 - TIDAL WAVE (A): w/i 120' cause up to 30'Lx10'Hx1'T. 4d8 & prone or DEX for 1/2
3 - DISPEL MAGIC (A): 1 target w/i 120', spell ends if < 4th or WIS check (DC = 10+lvl)
4 - CONFUSION (A, 1m, c): All things w/i 10'r w/i 90' WIS save or confused
3 - CONJURE ANIMALS (A, 1hr, c): 1,2, 4, or 8 beats totaling 2 CR
3 - WATER BREATHING (A, 24hr, r): <= 10 allies w/i 30' breathe normal underwater
